quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  89,1,"Yaha! M (Mani Naawuni) po yuŋ yuŋ pia."
  89,2,"Yaha! M (Mani Naawuni) po binjiɛhi, ni bingaŋsi."
  89,3,"Yaha! M (Mani Naawuni) po yuŋ, di yi ti yɛn chaŋ yεɣi."
  89,4,"Achiika! Di puuni mali pɔri nzaŋ ti ninvuɣu so ŋun mali haŋkali?"
  89,5,"Di ni bɔŋɔ, a bi nya a Duuma ni daa niŋ Aadunim’ (Annabi Hudu niriba) shɛm?"
  89,6,"Bana n-nyɛ Iramanim’ ban nama daa galsi galsi."
  89,7,"Ka bɛ daa nyɛla bɛ ni na ʒin nam shɛba tatabo tiŋgbana ni."
  89,8,"Ni Samuudunim’ ban daa ŋmari tampima (ka di leeri yiya) yiliŋ ni."
  89,9,"Ni Fir’auna so ŋun nyɛ bandilana."
  89,10,"Bana n-nyɛ ban kpahi yεɣi tariga tiŋgbana ni."
  89,11,"Ka bɛ zooi tuumbiɛri tumbu di puuni."
  89,12,"Ka a Duuma kpaai azaaba balibu m-bahi bɛ zuɣu."
  89,13,"Achiika! A Duuma nyɛla Ŋun pa nina yuunda."
  89,14,"A nya ninsala, o Duuma yi dahimmi o ka tibgi o, ka niŋ o"
  89,15,"ni’ima shɛli, o yɛrimi: “Achiika! N Duuma shiri tibgi ma.”"
  89,16,"Amaa! O yi ti dahimmi o ka chɛ ka bɛhigu kpɛm n-ti o, o yɛri mi: “N Duuma filim ma.”"
  89,17,"Haifa! Chɛli gba! Yi bi tibgirila kpibga."
  89,18,"Yi mi bi kpaŋsiri ni nandana dihibu."
  89,19,"Ka yi diri fali liɣiri dibu din zooi."
  89,20,"Ka yi lahi yuri liɣiri yurlim din zooi."
  89,21,"Haifa! Bɛ yi ti dam tiŋgbani dambu ni yɛlimaŋli."
  89,22,"Ka a Duuma kana, ka Malaaikanim’ ti ʒe safu ni."
  89,23,"Dindali ka bɛ yɛn ti zaŋ ʒahannama buɣum na, dindali ka ninsala yɛn ti teei, ka yapolo ka teebu yɛn niŋ o anfaani."